### Setup New Relic for Next.js with NODE_OPTIONS

Source: https://github.com/newrelic/node-newrelic/blob/main/README.md

Starts a Next.js application with the New Relic agent automatically loaded via the NODE_OPTIONS environment variable. This is the recommended method for instrumenting Next.js applications.

```bash
NODE_OPTIONS='-r newrelic' next start
```

