### Handle arrays of functions when wrapping middleware mounters

Source: https://github.com/newrelic/node-newrelic/blob/main/NEWS.md

This fix resolves an issue where the agent incorrectly assumed that arrays passed as the first argument in middleware would only contain route paths, which caused a fatal error. The agent now correctly handles arrays of functions when wrapping middleware.

```javascript
app.use([middleware1, middleware2], function(req, res, next) {
  // ...
});
```

