### Add option for using the finally method on promises

Source: https://github.com/newrelic/node-newrelic/blob/main/NEWS.md

An option has been added to use the 'finally' method on promises for instrumentation. This addresses an issue with Node v10 promises causing infinite recursion due to calling 'then' inside their 'finally' method.

```javascript
promise.finally(() => {
  // ...
});
```

