### Update WebFrameworkShim to handle arrays of routes in middleware

Source: https://github.com/newrelic/node-newrelic/blob/main/NEWS.md

The WebFrameworkShim has been updated to handle arrays of routes when wrapping middleware mounters. This ensures accurate transaction naming even when using shared middleware with multiple routes.

```javascript
app.use(['/one', '/two'], ...)
```

