### Update Opensearch Instrumentation to Subscribe to Events in Node.js

Source: https://github.com/newrelic/node-newrelic/blob/main/NEWS.md

Refactors the Opensearch instrumentation to subscribe to emitted events, improving how instrumentation is handled. This change removes the `id` parameter from the `opensearch` class.

```javascript
// Previous implementation might have looked like this:
// const opensearch = new Opensearch(config, id);

// New implementation subscribes to events, id parameter removed.
